          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-tight">
            Your
            <span class="block bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              Wholesale
            </span>
            Partner for
            <span class="block text-white/90">Success</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-xl text-blue-200 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
            Supplying premium products across personal care, beverages, household goods, and more with next-day delivery across the UK.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
